```

### Interface Must Return

```python
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class LoanLimitAssessmentResult:
    application_id: UUID
    shareholding_based_limit: Decimal
    land_based_limit: Decimal
    final_eligible_amount: Decimal
    requested_amount: Decimal
    exceeds_limit: bool
